snippet.title: ROMA - Teremsha Bunduki  (Official Audio)
snippet.description:
Intro

Ambaa weee x 8

Ambaaaa weeenaa x 4

Chorus

Afande teremsha bunduki/

Unaowatetea mbona hawakukumbuki/

Unatuonea unatupiga mabuti/

Mara virungu mara unataka kutushuti/ Eeeeee 

*2

*Hook*

Afande teremshaaaaaa 
(Haaaaai Haii Haii)

Afande teremsha bunduki (Haii Haii)

*4


*Verse 1*

Anaye andamana hana sindano wala kiwembe/

So kumuua muandamanaji sio ushujaa huo ni uzembe/

Mnabeba silaha nzito akili zenu zisiwe nyepesi/

Jeshi ni wito sio muujiza wa kupuliza gesi/

Nyie mnavunja amani/
Mnapiga raia mahakamani/
Mwisho wapoteze imani/
Waamue kumalizana mtaani/

Hamuheshimu muhimili/
Nyie makatili hamna maadili/
Hamstahili injili/
Labda albadir tena alfajiri/

Wanaofaidika boss zenu sio nyie askari wa chini/

Kwa posho ndogo mnatumwa mtupige sasa kwanini/

Yaani unamuua anayepambania kesho bora ya mwanao/

Huku unamlinda anayekuibia na ukistaafu hakupi mafao/

Watoto wao wana mali/
Wanaendesha bugatti ferrari/
We askari chakari/
Unadaiwa kwa mangi sukari/
Na hauna gari/
Tunagombania mwendokasi ni hatari/
Tukidai mabasi unatupiga risasi we ndo’ muasi/

Hook


*Verse 2*

Unayemuona adui unampiga ndio anaekulipa mshahara/

Ndio mwalimu wa mwanao ndio nesi aliyekufanyia tohara/

Ungana nasi hizo bunduki sio za kumlinda mtawala/

Anayetuibia na kututeka huku akihubiri 4R/

Tuna jobless laki tano anaahidi ajira elfu saba/

Na mnashangilia october mtatiki mtapigwa mnada/

Kama ameshindwa miaka minne ndio ataweza siku mia/

Kafeli bima mnadanganywa kitoto nawahurumia/

Hawaheshimu hata wajumbe ndio chanzo cha hizi vurugu/

Maana wanapitisha wabunge ambao wanaweza kuwamudu/

Tusiruhusu huu uchaguzi/
Ni uchafuzi na ulanguzi/
Wa kipuuzi mashuzi/
Wame-loose fuse/
Wamekata pumzi

*Chorus*

*Hook*

¡Hey, yeah!

Empezamos lento, después salvaje

Pasito a pasito, suave suavecito

Nos vamo' pegando, poquito a poquito (Oh-oh)

Pero pa' montarlo aquí tengo la pieza, oye (Yo, yo; ¡plo!)

Firmar las paredes de tu laberinto
Y hacer de tu cuerpo todo un manuscrito
(Sube, sube, sube), ah (Sube, sube)

Quiero ver bailar tu pelo, quiero ser tu ritmo 
Que le enseñes a mi boca (Woah, woah)
Tus lugares favoritos (Favorito', favorito', baby)
Déjame sobrepasar tus zonas de peligro 
Hasta provocar tus gritos (Woah, woah)
Y que olvides tu apellido

[Puente: Luis Fonsi]
Despacito, Vamo' a hacerlo en una playa en Puerto Rico
Hasta que las olas griten: "¡Ay, bendito!"
Para que mi sello se quede contigo

Pasito a pasito, suave suavecito 
Nos vamos pegando, poquito a poquito 
Que le enseñes a mi boca
Tus lugares favoritos
Favorito', favorito', baby (Ooh)

Nos vamos pegando, poquito a poquito

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner Swap VS 2 Hunters
snippet.description:
This was crazy intense. Manhunt, but with a twist.

This video, I teamed up with a Manhunt NOOB, Dr Donut, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic


In this challenge Dr Donut and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.

This is one of my first ever collabs of this type, if you'd like to see more, like the video!

This was played on Minecraft 1.21.8, and is a custom coded challenge. There were a few bugs that we plan to iron out before we try something like this again!

200,000 likes for me to try this challenge with someone else!


DrDonut: @DrDonutt 
Skeppy: @Skeppy 
Daquavis: @DaquavisMC 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken
